sourceMeaningMnemonic: The <radical>narwhal</radical> and the <radical>turkey</radical> are meeting in <radical>private</radical> to uh, show each other some private things. Doing this they realize they're both <kanji>male</kanji>!
meaningInfo: Picture a male narwhal and a male turkey meeting together in private. Whispering. Giggling. Pointing at each other's male bits.
readingMnemonic: These <kanji>male</kanji> animals are obviously experimenting with things still. Ah, they must be <reading>you</reading>ths (<ja>ゆう</ja>)!  To be a youth, again!
readingInfo: It's just nature. Youths like to learn and try new things. And if two male youth animals wanna get together in private that's their business.
